Trust Your Kid’s Digestive Health to Culturelle. Culturelle Kids Multivitamins are natural fruit punch-flavored multivitamins formulated with 11 essential vitamins and minerals, are an excellent source of the antioxidants vitamins A & E, and contain a good source of zinc.

What are Culturelle Kids Multivitamin + Probiotic Chewables? They are chewable supplements for kids, offering both vitamins and probiotics. What probiotic strains do they contain? They contain Lactobacillus GG for digestive health support. How many chewables should my child take? Children should take one chewable per day. What age range should children be to take this chewable? Children ages 3 to 12 can take the product. How long should my child use these chewables? These can be used as part of a daily wellness routine.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 29, 2024
reviews.reviewText: Great tasting. Like the all in one multi vitamin and probiotic.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 27, 2023
reviews.reviewText: These are great. Kids like the taste and seem to help balance out vitamin needs for kids.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 22, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Low Sugar Vitamins
reviews.reviewText: I was looking for a replacement for Olly brand after they removed the sugar coating only to increase the sugar content. I decided to give these a try and am very happy we made the switch! My kids love the taste of these vitamins and I love that they are low sugar and still have everything we want in a vitamin.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 1, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars expensive but worth it
reviews.reviewText: I like that this is a non refrigerated probiotic for kids, we took two packs with us to Nicaragua for my kids. They stayed healthy. Great for travel.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 24, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Multivitamin and Probiotic in One for kids!
reviews.reviewText: My daughter had such struggles with pooping since she was a toddler! She would hold it and then run away and hide! I was on the hunt for a good probiotic for her and came across this one, which with an added benefit had a multivitamin source in it! My daughter loves these and prefers these over any other brand. She is now regular and I don't have to worry about if she's pooped or not!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 12, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Kids like them
reviews.reviewText: My kids like the way these taste, but I was not impressed with the probiotic portion. They don’t seem to work as well as the just straight Culturelle probiotics that I bought before these. I like that they come with a multivitamin in there too but I think I won’t buy them again

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 5, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars My kids actually like these
reviews.reviewText: My children are super picky. ALL THREE of them actually ASK for these and they have great ingredients. I will purchase these again.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 8, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Finally a probiotic my kids enjoy! (I like them, too)
reviews.reviewText: These are tasty. The kids don't even realize they are taking something healthy... parent win!

reviews.reviewTitle: Genial sabor y presentación para niños
reviews.reviewText: A mejorado el apetito de mi hija y le encanta el sabor y la presentación de las vitaminas. Había probado otras pero al ser aceitosas y diluirse en jugo no se la tomaba en todas las ocasiones.
My kids love the taste and willingly take it all the time
